patientCountrySearchParameter

Parameter address-country:string

Searches based on the patient's recorded country of address eg) /ws/fhir2/{release}/Patient?address-country={country}

ResourcePatient
Expression(none)
Target ResourcesPatient
MultiplesThe parameter cannot repeat or have multiple values
